title: Nylon Blue Spatula Set of 3
description: No kitchen should be without these handy tools. Built like a spatula with a shallow spoon shape on one side, it's perfect for a variety of tasks from mixing and folding to serving and scraping. This set comes with 3 different sizes for all your needs and will quickly become one of your favorite kitchen tools!High heat silicone heads are heat-safe to 500 degrees FDishwasher-safeDishwasher-safeCaution: handles may melt if rested on the side of a hot pan
